    <note>Li(2) Gao(5) [22466] An official of the Northern Liang. he founded the state of Xiliang (Western Liang), the weakest of the 16 kingdoms of the Jin dynasty period. As prefect of Dunhuang, in 400 A.D., he proclaimed himself Duke of Xiliang. The state was soon conquered by Northern Liang after Gao's death. See entry for Xiliang in Morihashi.</note>
